## Citing the tool

> Omena, J. J. (2026). *AI Source Scraper* [Computer software]. Zenodo.
> https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20945556

The tool never sends data anywhere: all scanning happens in your browser,
and files are saved locally by you. It makes zero network requests.
